      "value": "<p>At 15th level, once per day, you can unravel the fibers of reality and ride along them as they snap back into place. This power functions as @Compendium[pf1.spells.ojwg1ki98tq8xyh9]{Dimension Door}, while also creating a mass of @Compendium[pf1.spells.wralcmyi4tdcai24]{Black Tentacles}&nbsp;centered on your former location. Both of these effects use your sorcerer level as the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Caster-Level\">caster level</a>. At 20th level, you can use this ability twice per day.</p>",
